==
- Its intended to be deployed on EVM based chains.
==

==
- The project aims to provide users to communicate anonymously based on events.
==

=============== 
WEB3 jobs

==
A conversation gets started by a user paying a small fee once, the messages get hashed client side, and get sent to the the conversation, which then emits an event.
==

==
The events get caught by our web-interface, depending on the conversation the user intends to read.
==

==
Its the responsibility of the user to send the encryption key off chain to the intended recipient to able to decode the messages
==

===============
WEB2 jobs

==
The interface may provide the option to store the encryption key in cookies, to prevent inputting it everytime, to decode a message

WARNING!
its not recommended to store encryption key, in your cookies, as it opens doors to XSS attacks from malicious extensions, and potential malwares.
===============